title: Miunohri to Swan
description: She is a fat ugly girl with a short body; she's a girl who used to be a loner, loser and always hated by everyone. It only takes one of a stranger's 'abracadabras' to turn her into a beauty and to stop the bullying. Though it comes with a price: she can't kiss "him" or go under any rain, or she'll become ugly again.
